1. Make sure the "cmvs_dep" is compiled.

2. Edit two environment variables "CMVS_TOP" and "CMVS_DEP" in the "settings64.sh".

3. Type this command to source the settings: source settings64.sh

4. To compile, type command: ./install_all.sh

5. To test, type command: ./test.sh
   The result is generated at "cmvs/core/bundler/bundler-v0.4-source/pmvs/models/option-0000.ply", which can be viewed by the open source software "MeshLab".

6. Do not forget to source the settings again if you have logged out.
